<span style='float: right; width: 280px; height: 187px; margin: 0 0 5px 5px; border: 1px solid black;'><script type='text/javascript'>flash_object ('http://graphics.millsberry.com/buddy/buddy_featured.swf', '280', '187', 'userName=ooee5&buddyTimeStamp=20060508&buddyScriptURL=http%3A%2F%2Fmillsberry.com%2Fbuddy%2Fprocess_buddy.phtml&unixTimeStamp=1193060212&serverTimeOffset=28800', '', 'exactfit', 'transparent');</script></span>
Meet <b>Ooee5</b>, our citizen of the week!<br><br>Ooee5 lives at <a href='/home/?user=ooee5'>15164 Willow Wood Way</a> in one of the stately historical homes in Ravenwood.  He has enjoyed learning about his neighborhood's rich history since he moved there on November 10, 2005.  <br><br>You wouldn't know it just by looking at him, but Ooee5 has one of the sharpest minds in Millsberry!  The secret behind his amazing mental abilities is his keen observation skills.  By keeping a close eye on his environment at all times, Ooee5 sees a lot of things that other people might skip over.  His observant and inquisitive nature has really helped him in his favorite area of interest - computers.  Ooee5 can work through the most complex computer problem simply by paying close attention and making a mental note of everything the computer is doing.<br><br>Ooee5 puts his observation skills to good use in his drawing as well, which is another one of his favorite hobbies.  Ooee5 especially enjoys drawing animals, but he likes to express his creativity by giving his pictures wild colors, such as gold, silver, and zebra print.  Although both of his favorite pastimes are mostly indoor pursuits, Ooee5 still manages to find time to get outdoors and participate in sports, and he has a shelf full of trophies to prove his athleticism!  He'll often stay after classes have let out for the day at <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/academy">Millsberry Academy</a> to practice his baseball moves with Coach Danner.  On other days, Ooee5 heads to <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/peabody_park">Peabody Park</a> for an exciting game of hockey or basketball.<br><br>When Ooee5 just wants to kick back with his friends, he usually goes to a mall for some browsing and relaxing.  His favorite store to visit is the music store, where he enjoys shuffling through all the latest heavy metal, classical, and rap CDs and listening to samples from them.  Ooee5 has a very sophisticated ear, and he definitely knows what he likes!<br><br>Thanks for being a fine citizen, Ooee5, and congratulations on being named Millsberry's Citizen of the Week!</div>
